      "id": 43420,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "The video upload endpoint on the TikTok Ads portal was potentially susceptible to remote code execution (RCE) due to a ffmpeg misconfiguration. We thank @ bubbounty for reporting this to our team and confirming the resolution. ",
